subproject.description: The project is for the implementation of the Global Fund Round 6 HIV/AIDS Grant (LBR-607-G04-H). The objectives The following are the objectives defined for the current Grant include: (i) reduce the number of new HIV/AIDS/STI infections among the general population and vulnerable target groups; (ii) reduce morbidity and mortality among adults and children living with HIV/AIDS by scaling-up HIV treatment, care and support; (iii) strengthen  integration of  HIV/TB services and (iv) strengthen health systems and program management needed to build capacity and support the expansion and effective implementation of HIV/AIDS services nationwide
